{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775904331691,"sessionID":"ses_283daa7d5ffetel4o904WBlsNl","part":{"id":"prt_d7c2592f10013ZUIJj72qyTYb9","messageID":"msg_d7c25784b001k6ZSYBB02C9HrV","sessionID":"ses_283daa7d5ffetel4o904WBlsNl","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-eed0bc168981465f9e321344285701c7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-042/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-042/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 |\n8: | Module | docs |\n9: | Language | TypeScript |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 (completed) |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Architecture\n16: \n17: ### Component Overview\n18: \n19: ```\n20: docs/\n21: ├── docusaurus.config.ts     # Core configuration (site metadata, plugins, theme)\n22: ├── sidebars.ts              # Sidebar navigation structure\n23: ├── package.json             # npm dependencies and scripts\n24: ├── tsconfig.json            # TypeScript configuration\n25: ├── src/\n26: │   ├── pages/\n27: │   │   └── index.tsx        # Homepage component\n28: │   └── css/\n29: │   │   └── custom.css       # Custom styles and branding\n30: │   └── components/          # Custom React components\n31: │   └── theme/               # Theme overrides\n32: ├── docs/\n33: │   ├── architecture/\n34: │   │   ├── overview.md      # System architecture overview\n35: │   │   ├── sandbox.md       # Sandbox orchestration details\n36: │   │   ├── session-routing.md\n37: │   │   └── idle-cleanup.md\n38: │   ├── api/\n39: │   │   ├── sdk-python/\n40: │   │   │   ├── client.md    # Python SDK API reference\n41: │   │   │   └── examples.md\n42: │   │   └── client-go/\n43: │   │       ├── overview.md  # Go client API reference\n44: │   │       └── examples.md\n45: │   ├── deployment/\n46: │   │   ├── kubernetes.md    # K8s deployment guide\n47: │   │   ├── helm-chart.md    # Helm chart parameters\n48: │   │   └── configuration.md\n49: │   ├── getting-started/\n50: │   │   ├── installation.md  # Prerequisites and setup\n51: │   │   ├── first-sandbox.md # Quick-start tutorial\n52: │   │   ├── configuration.md\n53: │   │   └── next-steps.md\n54: │   └── changelog/\n55: │       ├── index.md         # Release history\n56: │       ├── v0.1.0.md\n57: │       └── v0.2.0.md\n58: ├── static/\n59: │   ├── img/\n60: │   │   ├── logo.svg         # Project logo\n61: │   │   ├── architecture-diagrams/\n62: │   │   └── screenshots/\n63: │   └── favicon.ico\n64: ├── i18n/\n65: │   ├── en/                  # English translations\n66: │   └── zh-Hans/             # Chinese translations\n67: └── build/                   # Production build output\n68: ```\n69: \n70: ### Component Interactions\n71: \n72: ```\n73: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n74: │                           Docusaurus Site Architecture                         │\n75: ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n76: │                                                                               │\n77: │  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n78: │  │ docusaurus.config.ts│────▶│              Plugin Chain                    │ │\n79: │  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌───────────────────────┐  │ │\n80: │  │ - siteMetadata      │     │  │ preset-     │  │ theme-search-algolia  │  │ │\n81: │  │ - themeConfig       │     │  │ classic     │  │ plugin-search-local   │  │ │\n82: │  │ - plugins           │     │  └─────────────┘  └───────────────────────┘  │ │\n83: │  │ - presets           │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n84: │  └─────────────────────┘     │  │ content-docs, content-blog, sitemap    │ │ │\n85: │                              │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n86: │                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n87: │                                                                               │\n88: │  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n89: │  │ sidebars.ts         │────▶│              Navigation                     │ │\n90: │  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n91: │  │ - gettingStarted    │     │  │ Sidebar Categories                      │ │ │\n92: │  │ - architecture      │     │  │  ├── Getting Started                    │ │ │\n93: │  │ - api               │     │  │  ├── Architecture                       │ │ │\n94: │  │ - deployment        │     │  │  ├── API Reference                      │ │ │\n95: │  │ - changelog         │     │  │  ├── Deployment                         │ │ │\n96: │  │                     │     │  │  └── Changelog                          │ │ │\n97: │  └─────────────────────┘     │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n98: │                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n99: │                                                                               │\n100: │  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n101: │  │ src/pages/          │────▶│              Page Rendering                 │ │\n102: │  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n103: │  │ - index.tsx         │     │  │ React Pages                             │ │ │\n104: │  │ - custom pages      │     │  │  ├── Homepage (Hero + CTA)              │ │ │\n105: │  │                     │     │  │  ├── Version Selector                   │ │ │\n106: │  │                     │     │  │  └── Language Switcher                  │ │ │\n107: │  └─────────────────────┘     │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n108: │                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n109: │                                                                               │\n110: │  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n111: │  │ docs/**/*.md        │────▶│              Content Processing             │ │\n112: │  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n113: │  │ - frontmatter       │     │  │ Markdown → React                        │ │ │\n114: │  │ - Mermaid diagrams  │     │  │  ├── MDX processing                     │ │ │\n115: │  │ - code examples     │     │  │  ├── Mermaid rendering                  │ │ │\n116: │  │                     │     │  │  ├── Code highlighting                  │ │ │\n117: │  └─────────────────────┘     │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n118: │                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n119: │                                                                               │\n120: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ### Build and Deployment Flow\n124: \n125: ```\n126: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n127: │                          Build & Deployment Pipeline                          │\n128: ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n129: │                                                                               │\n130: │  ┌───────────────────┐                                                       │\n131: │  │ Source Files      │                                                       │\n132: │  │ docs/**/*.md      │                                                       │\n133: │  │ src/**/*.tsx      │                                                       │\n134: │  └───────────────────┘                                                       │\n135: │           │                                                                   │\n136: │           ▼                                                                   │\n137: │  ┌───────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n138: │  │ npm run build     │────▶│              Build Steps                     │  │\n139: │  │                   │     │  1. TypeScript compilation                   │  │\n140: │  │                   │     │  2. Markdown → React components              │  │\n141: │  │                   │     │  3. Asset optimization                       │  │\n142: │  │                   │     │  4. Static HTML generation                   │  │\n143: │  │                   │     │  5. Search index creation                    │  │\n144: │  └───────────────────┘     └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n145: │           │                                                                   │\n146: │           ▼                                                                   │\n147: │  ┌───────────────────┐                                                       │\n148: │  │ build/            │                                                       │\n149: │  │ (static site)     │                                                       │\n150: │  └───────────────────┘                                                       │\n151: │           │                                                                   │\n152: │           ▼                                                                   │\n153: │  ┌───────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n154: │  │ GitHub Actions    │────▶│              Deploy                          │  │\n155: │  │ docs.yml          │     │  gh-pages branch OR custom domain            │  │\n156: │  └───────────────────┘     └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n157: │                                                                               │\n158: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ---\n162: \n163: ## Data Structures\n164: \n165: ### Docusaurus Configuration Interface\n166: \n167: ```typescript\n168: interface DocusaurusConfig {\n169:   title: string;\n170:   tagline: string;\n171:   url: string;\n172:   baseUrl: string;\n173:   favicon: string;\n174:   organizationName: string;\n175:   projectName: string;\n176:   trailingSlash: boolean;\n177:   onBrokenLinks: 'throw' | 'warn';\n178:   onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'throw' | 'warn';\n179:   i18n: {\n180:     defaultLocale: string;\n181:     locales: string[];\n182:   };\n183:   presets: PresetConfig[];\n184:   plugins: PluginConfig[];\n185:   themeConfig: ThemeConfig;\n186: }\n187: ```\n188: \n189: ### Theme Configuration\n190: \n191: ```typescript\n192: interface ThemeConfig {\n193:   navbar: NavbarConfig;\n194:   footer: FooterConfig;\n195:   prism: PrismConfig;\n196:   algolia?: AlgoliaConfig;\n197:   docs: DocsThemeConfig;\n198: }\n199: \n200: interface NavbarConfig {\n201:   title: string;\n202:   logo: LogoConfig;\n203:   items: NavbarItem[];\n204: }\n205: \n206: interface NavbarItem {\n207:   type?: 'doc' | 'docSidebar' | 'docsVersion' | 'localeDropdown' | 'search';\n208:   label: string;\n209:   to?: string;\n210:   href?: string;\n211:   docsPluginId?: string;\n212:   sidebarId?: string;\n213:   position?: 'left' | 'right';\n214: }\n215: \n216: interface FooterConfig {\n217:   style: 'dark' | 'light';\n218:   links: FooterLinkSection[];\n219:   logo?: LogoConfig;\n220:   copyright: string;\n221: }\n222: \n223: interface FooterLinkSection {\n224:   title: string;\n225:   items: FooterLink[];\n226: }\n227: \n228: interface FooterLink {\n229:   label: string;\n230:   to?: string;\n231:   href?: string;\n232: }\n233: ```\n234: \n235: ### Sidebar Configuration\n236: \n237: ```typescript\n238: interface SidebarsConfig {\n239:   gettingStarted: SidebarItem[];\n240:   architecture: SidebarItem[];\n241:   api: SidebarItem[];\n242:   deployment: SidebarItem[];\n243:   changelog: SidebarItem[];\n244: }\n245: \n246: interface SidebarItem {\n247:   type: 'doc' | 'category' | 'link' | 'generated-index';\n248:   id?: string;\n249:   label: string;\n250:   items?: SidebarItem[];\n251:   link?: {\n252:     type: 'generated-index' | 'doc';\n253:     id?: string;\n254:     slug?: string;\n255:     description?: string;\n256:   };\n257:   className?: string;\n258:   customProps?: Record<string, unknown>;\n259: }\n260: ```\n261: \n262: ### Document Frontmatter Schema\n263: \n264: ```typescript\n265: interface DocFrontmatter {\n266:   id: string;\n267:   title: string;\n268:   description?: string;\n269:   slug?: string;\n270:   sidebar_label?: string;\n271:   sidebar_position?: number;\n272:   hide_title?: boolean;\n273:   hide_table_of_contents?: boolean;\n274:   toc_min_heading_level?: number;\n275:   toc_max_heading_level?: number;\n276:   pagination_prev?: string | null;\n277:   pagination_next?: string | null;\n278:   last_update?: {\n279:     date: string;\n280:     author: string;\n281:   };\n282:   keywords?: string[];\n283:   tags?: string[];\n284: }\n285: ```\n286: \n287: ### i18n Locale Configuration\n288: \n289: ```typescript\n290: interface LocaleConfig {\n291:   label: string;\n292:   direction: 'ltr' | 'rtl';\n293:   htmlLang: string;\n294: }\n295: ```\n296: \n297: ---\n298: \n299: ## API Contracts\n300: \n301: ### Site Configuration Contract\n302: \n303: **docusaurus.config.ts Required Fields:**\n304: \n305: | Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |\n306: |-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|\n307: | `title` | `string` | Yes | - | Site title displayed in navbar |\n308: | `tagline` | `string` | Yes | - | Site description for SEO |\n309: | `url` | `string` | Yes | - | Production deployment URL |\n310: | `baseUrl` | `string` | Yes | `/` | Base path for deployment |\n311: | `favicon` | `string` | Yes | - | Relative path to favicon |\n312: | `organizationName` | `string` | Yes | - | GitHub organization name |\n313: | `projectName` | `string` | Yes | - | GitHub project name |\n314: \n315: **Contract:**\n316: - `url` SHALL be `https://volcano-sh.github.io`\n317: - `baseUrl` SHALL be `/agentcube/`\n318: - `title` SHALL be `AgentCube`\n319: - `tagline` SHALL describe sandbox orchestration purpose\n320: \n321: ### Navigation Contract\n322: \n323: **Navbar Items Required:**\n324: \n325: | Label | Target | Position |\n326: |-------|--------|----------|\n327: | Documentation | `/docs` | left |\n328: | API Reference | `/docs/api` | left |\n329: | Architecture | `/docs/architecture` | left |\n330: | Deployment | `/docs/deployment` | left |\n331: | Getting Started | `/docs/getting-started` | left |\n332: | GitHub | `https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` | right |\n333: \n334: **Contract:**\n335: - Each navbar item SHALL have valid `to` or `href`\n336: - Navbar SHALL be responsive for mobile devices\n337: - Logo SHALL link to homepage\n338: \n339: ### Sidebar Contract\n340: \n341: **Sidebar Categories Required:**\n342: \n343: | Category | Document IDs | Order |\n344: |----------|--------------|-------|\n345: | `gettingStarted` | `installation`, `first-sandbox`, `configuration`, `next-steps` | 1 |\n346: | `architecture` | `overview`, `sandbox`, `session-routing`, `idle-cleanup` | 2 |\n347: | `api` | `sdk-python/client`, `sdk-python/examples`, `client-go/overview`, `client-go/examples` | 3 |\n348: | `deployment` | `kubernetes`, `helm-chart`, `configuration` | 4 |\n349: | `changelog` | `index`, `v0.1.0`, `v0.2.0` | 5 |\n350: \n351: **Contract:**\n352: - Sidebar SHALL auto-generate from `docs/**/*.md` files\n353: - Items SHALL be ordered by `sidebar_position` frontmatter\n354: - Categories SHALL have collapsible functionality\n355: \n356: ### Homepage Contract\n357: \n358: **Homepage Components Required:**\n359: \n360: | Component | Description |\n361: |-----------|-------------|\n362: | Hero Section | Project title, tagline, logo |\n363: | CTA Buttons | \"Get Started\" → `/docs/getting-started/installation`, \"View on GitHub\" → external |\n364: | Features Grid | 3-4 feature highlights with icons |\n365: | Footer | Links, copyright |\n366: \n367: **Contract:**\n368: - Homepage SHALL use Docusaurus `@theme/Layout` wrapper\n369: - Hero SHALL include gradient background\n370: - CTA buttons SHALL be prominent and accessible\n371: \n372: ---\n373: \n374: ## Error Handling\n375: \n376: ### Build Error Categories\n377: \n378: | Error Type | Source | Handling | Recovery |\n379: |------------|--------|----------|----------|\n380: | Broken Link | Markdown link resolution | Build fails with error | Fix link path |\n381: | Broken Markdown Link | Markdown link resolution | Build fails with error | Fix markdown link |\n382: | Invalid Frontmatter | YAML parsing | Build fails with error | Fix YAML syntax |\n383: | TypeScript Error | TSX compilation | Build fails with error | Fix TS errors |\n384: | Plugin Error | Plugin initialization | Build fails with error | Fix plugin config |\n385: | Asset Missing | Static file resolution | Build warning/fail | Add missing asset |\n386: \n387: ### Build Validation Errors\n388: \n389: ```typescript\n390: enum BuildErrorLevel {\n391:   THROW = 'throw',\n392:   WARN = 'warn',\n393:   IGNORE = 'ignore'\n394: }\n395: \n396: interface BrokenLinkError {\n397:   type: 'broken-link' | 'broken-markdown-link';\n398:   link: string;\n399:   file: string;\n400:   remediation: string;\n401: }\n402: ```\n403: \n404: **Configuration:**\n405: - `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'` - Hard fail on broken links\n406: - `onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'throw'` - Hard fail on broken markdown links\n407: \n408: ### Runtime Error Handling\n409: \n410: | Scenario | Error | User Impact | Mitigation |\n411: |----------|-------|-------------|------------|\n412: | Search unavailable | Algolia API error | Search disabled | Fallback to local search |\n413: | Language file missing | Missing i18n JSON | Default locale used | Log warning, continue |\n414: | Image not found | 404 on static assets | Missing image placeholder | Use placeholder, log warning |\n415: | Version not found | Invalid version path | 404 page | Redirect to latest |\n416: \n417: ### CI/CD Error Handling\n418: \n419: ```yaml\n420: # docs.yml workflow error handling\n421: jobs:\n422:   build:\n423:     steps:\n424:       - name: Build\n425:         run: npm run build\n426:         continue-on-error: false\n427:         \n428:       - name: Check build output\n429:         run: |\n430:           if [ ! -d \"build\" ]; then\n431:             echo \"Build directory not found\"\n432:             exit 1\n433:           fi\n434:           \n435:       - name: Validate links\n436:         run: npm run check-links || echo \"Link check completed\"\n437: ```\n438: \n439: ---\n440: \n441: ## Testing Strategy\n442: \n443: ### Unit Tests\n444: \n445: | Test | File | Scenario | Verification |\n446: |------|------|----------|--------------|\n447: | Config validation | `__tests__/config.test.ts` | Required fields present | All fields validated |\n448: | Sidebar structure | `__tests__/sidebar.test.ts` | Categories defined correctly | Navigation works |\n449: | Navbar items | `__tests__/navbar.test.ts` | Links are valid | No broken links |\n450: | Homepage render | `__tests__/index.test.ts` | Hero and CTA present | Components render |\n451: | TypeScript config | `__tests__/tsconfig.test.ts` | Strict mode enabled | TS compiles |\n452: | i18n setup | `__tests__/i18n.test.ts` | Locale directories exist | i18n works |\n453: \n454: ### Test Pattern\n455: \n456: ```typescript\n457: describe('DocusaurusConfig', () => {\n458:   it('should have required fields', () => {\n459:     const config = require('../docusaurus.config');\n460:     \n461:     expect(config.title).toBeDefined();\n462:     expect(config.tagline).toBeDefined();\n463:     expect(config.url).toBeDefined();\n464:     expect(config.baseUrl).toBeDefined();\n465:     expect(config.favicon).toBeDefined();\n466:     expect(config.organizationName).toBeDefined();\n467:     expect(config.projectName).toBeDefined();\n468:   });\n469:   \n470:   it('should have valid navbar items', () => {\n471:     const config = require('../docusaurus.config');\n472:     const items = config.themeConfig.navbar.items;\n473:     \n474:     expect(items.length).toBeGreaterThan(0);\n475:     items.forEach(item => {\n476:       expect(item.label).toBeDefined();\n477:       expect(item.to || item.href).toBeDefined();\n478:     });\n479:   });\n480:   \n481:   it('should have valid sidebar categories', () => {\n482:     const sidebars = require('../sidebars');\n483:     \n484:     expect(sidebars.gettingStarted).toBeDefined();\n485:     expect(sidebars.architecture).toBeDefined();\n486:     expect(sidebars.api).toBeDefined();\n487:     expect(sidebars.deployment).toBeDefined();\n488:     expect(sidebars.changelog).toBeDefined();\n489:   });\n490: });\n491: ```\n492: \n493: ### Integration Tests\n494: \n495: | Test | Scenario | Verification |\n496: |------|----------|--------------|\n497: | Local server start | `npm run start` | Dev server on port 3000 |\n498: | Production build | `npm run build` | Build directory created |\n499: | Links resolution | Navigate all pages | No 404 errors |\n500: | Search functionality | Query search bar | Results returned |\n501: | i18n switching | Change locale | Content translated |\n502: | Mermaid rendering | View architecture pages | Diagrams rendered |\n503: | Code highlighting | View API pages | Syntax highlighted |\n504: \n505: ### End-to-End Tests (Playwright/Cypress)\n506: \n507: ```typescript\n508: describe('Docs Site E2E', () => {\n509:   it('homepage should render correctly', async () => {\n510:     await page.goto('http://localhost:3000');\n511:     \n512:     await expect(page.locator('.hero__title')).toHaveText('AgentCube');\n513:     await expect(page.locator('.hero__cta')).toBeVisible();\n514:     await expect(page.locator('a[href=\"/docs/getting-started\"]')).toBeVisible();\n515:   });\n516:   \n517:   it('sidebar navigation should work', async () => {\n518:     await page.goto('http://localhost:3000/docs/architecture/overview');\n519:     \n520:     await page.click('[data-testid=\"sidebar-item-getting-started\"]');\n521:     await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\\/docs\\/getting-started/);\n522:   });\n523:   \n524:   it('search should return results', async () => {\n525:     await page.goto('http://localhost:3000');\n526:     await page.fill('.search-bar input', 'sandbox');\n527:     \n528:     await expect(page.locator('.search-result')).toBeVisible();\n529:   });\n530: });\n531: ```\n532: \n533: ### Test Coverage Goals\n534: \n535: | Area | Target Coverage |\n536: |------|------------------|\n537: | Config validation | 100% |\n538: | Navigation links | 100% (all links valid) |\n539: | Homepage components | >80% |\n540: | Build process | >70% |\n541: | Search integration | >60% |\n542: \n543: ### Validation Commands\n544: \n545: ```bash\n546: npm run build                    # Production build test\n547: npm run start                    # Dev server test\n548: npm run typecheck                # TypeScript validation\n549: npm run lint                     # ESLint validation\n550: npx playwright test              # E2E tests\n551: linkinator build/ --recursive    # Link validation\n552: ```\n553: \n554: ---\n555: \n556: ## File Structure\n557: \n558: ### Core Files\n559: \n560: | File | Action | Purpose |\n561: |------|--------|---------|\n562: | `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | create | Site configuration |\n563: | `docs/sidebars.ts` | create | Sidebar structure |\n564: | `docs/package.json` | create | Dependencies and scripts |\n565: | `docs/tsconfig.json` | create | TypeScript configuration |\n566: | `docs/.gitignore` | create | Ignore build output |\n567: | `docs/README.md` | create | Docs project README |\n568: \n569: ### Source Files\n570: \n571: | File | Action | Purpose |\n572: |------|--------|---------|\n573: | `docs/src/pages/index.tsx` | create | Homepage component |\n574: | `docs/src/css/custom.css` | create | Custom styling |\n575: | `docs/src/components/` | create | Custom React components |\n576: | `docs/src/theme/` | create | Theme overrides |\n577: \n578: ### Documentation Content\n579: \n580: | File | Action | Source |\n581: |------|--------|--------|\n582: | `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md` | create | From `design.md` |\n583: | `docs/docs/architecture/sandbox.md` | create | From `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` |\n584: | `docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md` | create | From `session-routing/design.md` |\n585: | `docs/docs/architecture/idle-cleanup.md` | create | From `idle-cleanup/design.md` |\n586: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/client.md` | create | From `sdk-python/` docs |\n587: | `docs/docs/api/client-go/overview.md` | create | From `client-go/` docs |\n588: | `docs/docs/deployment/kubernetes.md` | create | From `deployment/design.md` |\n589: | `docs/docs/deployment/helm-chart.md` | create | From `manifests/` charts |\n590: | `docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md` | create | New content |\n591: | `docs/docs/getting-started/first-sandbox.md` | create | New content |\n592: | `docs/docs/changelog/index.md` | create | From GitHub Releases |\n593: \n594: ### Static Assets\n595: \n596: | File | Action | Purpose |\n597: |------|--------|---------|\n598: | `docs/static/img/logo.svg` | create | Project logo |\n599: | `docs/static/img/favicon.ico` | create | Browser favicon |\n600: | `docs/static/img/architecture/*.svg` | create | Architecture diagrams |\n601: \n602: ### i18n Files\n603: \n604: | File | Action | Purpose |\n605: |------|--------|---------|\n606: | `docs/i18n/en/` | create | English translations |\n607: | `docs/i18n/zh-Hans/` | create | Chinese translations |\n608: \n609: ### CI/CD Files\n610: \n611: | File | Action | Purpose |\n612: |------|--------|---------|\n613: | `.github/workflows/docs.yml` | create | GitHub Actions workflow |\n614: \n615: ---\n616: \n617: ## Dependencies\n618: \n619: ### npm Dependencies\n620: \n621: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n622: |---------|---------|---------|\n623: | `@docusaurus/core` | `3.x` | Docusaurus core framework |\n624: | `@docusaurus/preset-classic` | `3.x` | Classic preset (docs, blog, pages) |\n625: | `@docusaurus/theme-search-algolia` | `3.x` | Algolia search integration |\n626: | `@docusaurus/plugin-search-local` | `latest` | Local search fallback |\n627: | `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases` | `3.x` | TypeScript type definitions |\n628: | `@docusaurus/types` | `3.x` | Core type definitions |\n629: | `react` | `18.x` | React frontend framework |\n630: | `react-dom` | `18.x` | React DOM renderer |\n631: | `typescript` | `5.x` | TypeScript compiler |\n632: \n633: ### Development Dependencies\n634: \n635: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n636: |---------|---------|---------|\n637: | `@types/react` | `18.x` | React type definitions |\n638: | `@types/react-dom` | `18.x` | React DOM type definitions |\n639: | `@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin` | `latest` | TypeScript ESLint |\n640: | `@typescript-eslint/parser` | `latest` | ESLint TypeScript parser |\n641: | `eslint` | `8.x` | JavaScript linter |\n642: | `prettier` | `3.x` | Code formatter |\n643: | `linkinator` | `latest` | Link checker |\n644: \n645: ### External Resources\n646: \n647: | Resource | URL | Purpose |\n648: |----------|-----|---------|\n649: | Algolia DocSearch | `https://docsearch.algolia.com/` | Search API credentials |\n650: | GitHub Pages | `https://pages.github.com/` | Static site hosting |\n651: | Mermaid CDN | `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid` | Diagram rendering |\n652: \n653: ---\n654: \n655: ## Implementation Notes\n656: \n657: ### Docusaurus Initialization\n658: \n659: ```bash\n660: npx create-docusaurus@latest docs classic --typescript\n661: cd docs\n662: npm install @docusaurus/plugin-search-local\n663: ```\n664: \n665: ### Configuration Values\n666: \n667: | Field | Value |\n668: |-------|-------|\n669: | `title` | `AgentCube` |\n670: | `tagline` | `Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agents` |\n671: | `url` | `https://volcano-sh.github.io` |\n672: | `baseUrl` | `/agentcube/` |\n673: | `organizationName` | `volcano-sh` |\n674: | `projectName` | `agentcube` |\n675: | `favicon` | `img/favicon.ico` |\n676: | `defaultLocale` | `en` |\n677: \n678: ### Sidebar Position Strategy\n679: \n680: Documents use frontmatter `sidebar_position` for ordering:\n681: \n682: ```markdown\n683: ---\n684: id: installation\n685: title: Installation\n686: sidebar_position: 1\n687: ---\n688: ```\n689: \n690: ### Mermaid Diagram Integration\n691: \n692: Docusaurus supports Mermaid diagrams in markdown:\n693: \n694: ```markdown\n695: ```mermaid\n696: graph TD\n697:     A[Client] --> B[Router]\n698:     B --> C[WorkloadManager]\n699:     C --> D[K8s API]\n700: ```\n701: ```\n702: \n703: ### Search Configuration Priority\n704: \n705: 1. Algolia DocSearch (if credentials available)\n706: 2. Local search plugin (fallback)\n707: \n708: ```typescript\n709: themeConfig: {\n710:   algolia: {\n711:     appId: process.env.ALGOLIA_APP_ID,\n712:     apiKey: process.env.ALGOLIA_API_KEY,\n713:     indexName: 'agentcube',\n714:   },\n715: }\n716: \n717: plugins: [\n718:   require.resolve('@docusaurus/plugin-search-local'),\n719: ]\n720: ```\n721: \n722: ### Makefile Integration\n723: \n724: ```makefile\n725: .PHONY: docs docs-start docs-clean\n726: \n727: docs:\n728: \tcd docs && npm run build\n729: \n730: docs-start:\n731: \tcd docs && npm run start\n732: \n733: docs-clean:\n734: \trm -rf docs/build docs/.docusaurus docs/node_modules\n735: ```\n736: \n737: ### GitHub Actions Workflow\n738: \n739: ```yaml\n740: name: Docs\n741: \n742: on:\n743:   push:\n744:     branches: [main]\n745:     paths: ['docs/**']\n746:   pull_request:\n747:     paths: ['docs/**']\n748: \n749: jobs:\n750:   build:\n751:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n752:     steps:\n753:       - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n754:       - uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n755:         with:\n756:           node-version: '18'\n757:           cache: 'npm'\n758:           cache-dependency-path: 'docs/package-lock.json'\n759:       - run: cd docs && npm ci\n760:       - run: cd docs && npm run build\n761:       - uses: actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3\n762:         with:\n763:           path: docs/build\n764: \n765:   deploy:\n766:     needs: build\n767:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n768:     if: github.event_name == 'push'\n769:     permissions:\n770:       pages: write\n771:       id-token: write\n772:     steps:\n773:       - uses: actions/deploy-pages@v4\n774: ```\n775: \n776: ---\n777: \n778: ## Validation Checklist\n779: \n780: - [x] Docusaurus project initialized with TypeScript template\n781: - [x] `docusaurus.config.ts` contains all required fields\n782: - [x] Navbar items link to valid documentation routes\n783: - [x] Sidebar categories and items resolve correctly\n784: - [x] Architecture pages render with Mermaid diagrams\n785: - [x] API reference pages include working code examples\n786: - [x] Deployment guide documents Kubernetes and Helm\n787: - [x] Getting started pages follow logical sequence\n788: - [x] Changelog page lists releases correctly\n789: - [x] Search integration configured (Algolia + local fallback)\n790: - [x] i18n directories initialized for zh-Hans\n791: - [x] GitHub Actions workflow triggers on docs changes\n792: - [x] Homepage renders with hero and CTA buttons\n793: - [x] Custom CSS applies branding styles\n794: - [x] Makefile docs targets defined\n795: - [x] Local dev server starts on port 3000\n796: - [x] Build output in `docs/build/` is valid static site\n797: \n798: ---\n799: \n800: ## References\n801: \n802: - Spec: `changes/AR-042/spec.md`\n803: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md`\n804: - Proposal: `changes/AR-042/proposal.md`\n805: - Tasks: `changes/AR-042/tasks.md`\n806: - [Docusaurus Official Docs](https://docusaurus.io/docs)\n807: - [Docusaurus TypeScript Support](https://docusaurus.io/docs/typescript)\n808: - [Algolia DocSearch](https://docsearch.algolia.com/)\n809: - [GitHub Pages Deployment](https://docusaurus.io/docs/deployment#github-pages)\n810: - Source docs: `design.md`, `sandbox-orchestration/design.md`, `deployment/design.md`\n811: - SDK sources: `sdk-python/`, `client-go/`\n\n(End of file - total 811 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 |\n| Module | docs |\n| Language | TypeScript |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 (completed) |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Overview\n\n```\ndocs/","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-042/design.md","time":{"start":1775904331662,"end":1775904331689}}}}
