{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775904818880,"sessionID":"ses_283daa7d5ffetel4o904WBlsNl","part":{"id":"prt_d7c2d064e001NY3gSh022NaTb4","messageID":"msg_d7c298fe6001MSvcZT8TroCO67","sessionID":"ses_283daa7d5ffetel4o904WBlsNl","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-3fb723cd5b5148efba4edfd500006b42","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 |\n| Module | docs |\n| Language | TypeScript |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Docusaurus Project Initialization (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Initialize Docusaurus project with TypeScript template\n  - Purpose: Create docs directory with classic preset\n  - Command: `npx create-docusaurus@latest docs classic --typescript`\n  - File: `docs/`\n  - Verification: `test -d docs`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Verify docs/docusaurus.config.ts exists\n  - Purpose: Confirm TypeScript config generated\n  - File: `docs/docusaurus.config.ts`\n  - Verification: `test -f docs/docusaurus.config.ts`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Verify docs/sidebars.ts exists\n  - Purpose: Confirm sidebar config generated\n  - File: `docs/sidebars.ts`\n  - Verification: `test -f docs/sidebars.ts`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Verify docs/package.json exists\n  - Purpose: Confirm npm package config generated\n  - File: `docs/package.json`\n  - Verification: `test -f docs/package.json`\n\n- [ ] **T1.5**: Verify docs/tsconfig.json exists\n  - Purpose: Confirm TypeScript config generated\n  - File: `docs/tsconfig.json`\n  - Verification: `test -f docs/tsconfig.json`\n\n- [ ] **T1.6**: Verify docs/src/pages/index.tsx exists\n  - Purpose: Confirm homepage component generated\n  - File: `docs/src/pages/index.tsx`\n  - Verification: `test -f docs/src/pages/index.tsx`\n\n- [ ] **T1.7**: Install local search plugin\n  - Purpose: Add fallback search capability\n  - Command: `cd docs && npm install @docusaurus/